    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a deep metallic red finish and a classic coupe silhouette. The body features smooth, aerodynamic curves, a long hood, and a compact rear, with a sharply raked windshield and a fastback roofline. The front end is characterized by pop-up style headlights, a small grille, and a subtle badge at the center. The side profile reveals two doors, flush door handles, and black multi-spoke alloy wheels with low-profile tires. The rear showcases a large rear window, dual exhaust pipes, and distinctive round taillights. The interior, visible through the windows, appears to have bucket seats and a minimalist dashboard, typical of high-performance sports cars.",
